title: “The Blacklist” (9 p.m., NBC): Let’s just call it “The Blacklist” road
text:
Tweet Published: Thu, October 15, 2015 @ 12:00 a.m. 
“The Blacklist” (9 p.m., NBC): Let’s just call it “The Blacklist” road show. This week, Red (James Spader) and Liz (Megan Boone) head for the Midwest in their ongoing quest to take down the Cabal and exonerate Liz. 
“Nathan For You” (10 p.m., Comedy Central): Season 3 begins. 
“Late Night Chef Fight” (9 p.m., FYI): Bone-in elk and pigskin are on the second-season premiere’s plate. 
TV listings, B6
